{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make all World War 2 veterans exempt from Tax and Care costs",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Our WW2 veterans are owed by us all. There are only 8 thousand alive. We need to look after them. No Tax on their Pensions at all. Their Care costs are free, paid by the Government.",
